{"tid":1869344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真係輸出革命] 有班中国人話要搞海外集會","createTime":"2020-02-08T06:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T05:24:20.000Z","uid":28759,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe0668e00b705c03311fdb9b7ac22ce8b9930bb","tid":1869344,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隨著李文亮去世的熱搜消失、死訊被確認，一波要求「言論自由」的討論迅速在微博上延燒。網友開始轉發《Do you hear the people sing》，截止7日凌晨1點12分，微博話題 #我要言論自由#共計收穫202.5萬閱讀量，超過8000條微博，該話題隨即被微博刪除。<br />\n<br />\n在刪除之前，不少網民表示：「如果謠言是他的罪名，我們唯有以真話悼念，我們不能，我們不明白，我們不原諒」。有網友轉發八九學潮時爭取言論自由的老照片，表示：「就算你我都明白，不會有變化的，但也要發聲，永遠要發聲。」甚至有網友效仿香港反修例運動的五大訴求提出了對應版的「五大訴求缺一不可」：「撤回對李文亮的訓誡；撤回所有刪帖命令；撤銷所有因言獲罪的指控；成立獨立調查委員會徹底追究涉事官員責任；立即歸還人民言論自由。」<br />\n<br />\n「我不想用各種縮寫同音詞來替換敏感詞，我想要正常說話。」<br />\n<br />\n「我希望終有一天我能走上街頭，舉著李醫生的照片。」<br />\n<br />\n摘自︰端傳媒 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200207-liwenliang-public-opinion/?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR2SysuL05mWevCQSg0oz32OFHJXKs0zvzaxu9cVoidyb8rcSTuk-1oTw5Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200207-liwenliang-public-opinion%2F%3Ffrom%3Dtimeline%26isappinstalled%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR2SysuL05mWevCQSg0oz32OFHJXKs0zvzaxu9cVoidyb8rcSTuk-1oTw5Y&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=2bf8c0e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200207-liwenliang-public-opinion/?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR2SysuL05mWevCQSg0oz32OFHJXKs0zvzaxu9cVoidyb8rcSTuk-1oTw5Y</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家海外中国公民仲想學我地搞「言論自由集會」<br />\n去中国領事館門外集會<br />\n口號「為真相吹哨」、「不能不明白」<br />\n品葱 post: <a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/13936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F13936&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=7964e892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/13936</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔係叫大家去</strong><br />\n但加個 hashtag<br />\n冷諷熱諷炒熱件事都好<br />\n<br />\n佢地嘅目的係爭取言論自由乜乜乜<br />\n我覺得大家可以推波助瀾下<br />\n我地可以趁呢個機會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">增加中国網絡維穩嘅成本</span></span></strong><br />\n幫中国政府燒下錢<br />\n何樂而不為？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸出革命 加速支爆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b1c85f6e6c6582c30207be8c5742adecf7b58ee1","tid":1869344,"uid":53413,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"敵人的敵人就是朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497f4dc0e3256a4d577cb95b6f2226edda3b98a7","tid":1869344,"uid":169195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:42:30.000Z","msg":"煲能大佢啦<br />\n理得佢上年講乜丫"},{"pid":"9ca9d7c817dafb80d1deb93ef41b2bdf564fcc27","tid":1869344,"uid":251168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"人民幣嘅發行量根本就冇公開過所以佢印幾多就幾多"},{"pid":"d88faf869c26c63703a8e331d878a6abd5e50c6e","tid":1869344,"uid":282359,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:46:34.000Z","msg":"誰理你 死光最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5fdcaf829ed9e0edfb2a426aa41af2e09c0093","tid":1869344,"uid":260296,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"d88faf869c26c63703a8e331d878a6abd5e50c6e","tid":1869344,"uid":282359,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:46:34.000Z","msg":"誰理你 死光最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:50:25.000Z","msg":"敵人嘅敵人 <br />\n<br />\n死光最好 但死法有好多種<br />\n<br />\n最好就係幫手擋子彈<br />\n<br />\n死光最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960da9f517017c8f856f62d4b1a238942ff3ccc6","tid":1869344,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:56:33.000Z","msg":"吹風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac